so you can't
get it wrong.

263
00:16:55,660 --> 00:16:57,071
All right?
So, simple.

264
00:16:57,140 --> 00:17:00,542
First of all, you push it into
the shoe with this.

265
00:17:01,020 --> 00:17:02,784
Unbelievable.

266
00:17:02,860 --> 00:17:05,545
If it isn't the mayor
of Base Camp!

267
00:17:05,620 --> 00:17:08,464
Scott Fischer,
Mr. Mountain Madness.

268
00:17:09,700 --> 00:17:10,781
In the flesh.

269
00:17:10,860 --> 00:17:12,350
You want a cup?

270
00:17:12,420 --> 00:17:15,742
Sit down, man.
Acclimatize!

