00:17:18,100 --> 00:17:19,465
but let's give it a go.

273
00:17:20,060 --> 00:17:21,744
Thank you so much.

274
00:17:27,260 --> 00:17:29,069
Wow. It's crazy
this year, eh?

275
00:17:29,900 --> 00:17:30,981
I know, man.

276
00:17:31,060 --> 00:17:33,666
Some idiot Kiwi goes and invents
Himalayan guiding

277
00:17:33,740 --> 00:17:35,902
and look what happens.

278
00:17:35,980 --> 00:17:38,586
