00:21:30,980 --> 00:21:31,947
You should start
feeling pretty good.

375
00:21:32,020 --> 00:21:33,021
I can feel it already.

376
00:21:33,100 --> 00:21:34,625
How did you boys go?

377
00:21:34,700 --> 00:21:36,065
Hey.
Instant happiness.

378
00:21:36,140 --> 00:21:38,188
- It's amazing.
- Very happy.

379
00:21:42,100 --> 00:21:43,829
Doug, you okay?

380
00:21:44,300 --> 00:21:45,500
Well, when we get
back to Base,

