00:21:45,540 --> 00:21:47,907
I want you to get Caro
to take a look at you.

382
00:21:48,020 --> 00:21:49,943
- No. I'm all right, I'm okay.
- No, no.

383
00:21:50,540 --> 00:21:52,110
And do me a favor,
spend your night on oxygen.

384
00:21:52,220 --> 00:21:53,426
Yeah?
Yeah.

385
00:21:53,500 --> 00:21:54,501
We got enough?

386
00:21:54,580 --> 00:21:56,469
We got plenty.
All right.

387
00:21:58,500 --> 00:22:00,707
Get some tea into ya.

388
00:22:01,340 --> 00:22:03,183
Just lift your
shirt up a bit.

389
00:22:03,260 --> 00:22:04,591
Thank you.

390
00:22:07,740 --> 00:22:09,663
And take a deep
breath for me?

391
00:22:16,020 --> 00:22:17,385
Just take one of those
in the morning

392
00:22:17,460 --> 00:22:18,791
