00:22:25,540 --> 00:22:27,190
Read it and weep.

396
00:22:27,740 --> 00:22:29,583
Take it
easy, Doug.

397
00:22:32,820 --> 00:22:34,549
Right, you can stop.
Yeah?

398
00:22:34,620 --> 00:22:35,621
You're in
great shape, Beck.

399
00:22:35,700 --> 00:22:36,701
I am in great shape.

400
00:22:37,140 --> 00:22:39,063
- You are.
- Six days a week in the gym.

