00:22:39,140 --> 00:22:41,302
Ought to do it.
Your wife must love that.

402
00:22:41,380 --> 00:22:42,381
Yeah, she does.

403
00:22:43,740 --> 00:22:46,141
Oh, no. What's
the date today?

