00:24:22,260 --> 00:24:24,308
<i>Wow! Really?</i>
Mmm-hmm.

445
00:24:24,820 --> 00:24:26,504
Get off!
<i>Peach?</i>

446
00:24:29,460 --> 00:24:31,508
I miss you, honey.

447
00:24:31,580 --> 00:24:33,582
Mom? Mom?

448
00:24:33,660 --> 00:24:35,310
<i>I miss the kids.</i>

449
00:24:37,140 --> 00:24:38,346
A lot.

450
00:24:40,420 --> 00:24:41,421
<i>Peach?</i>

451
00:24:41,500 --> 00:24:44,424
Listen, I gotta get
the kids to school

